2.0.5 - 2021-11-06
    Scroll bar in browser fragment

2.0.4 - 2021-11-06
    Bugfix: IllegalStateException in onSearch

2.0.3 - 2021-11-05
    Improved Google Assistant support

2.0.2 - 2021-10-29
    Ampache 5.0.0 compatibilty: tags vs. genres
    Reconnect when token expires
    "For You" now contains genres too
    New option: "For You" Mode
    Shuffle takes genre into account; songs are played in blocks of 2-5
    Minor UI updates

2.0.1 - 2021-10-19
    Bugfix: RuntimeException on LoudnessEnhancer.setTargetGain

2.0 - 2021-10-15
    Minimum Android version is now 9 Pie
    Replaced/rewrote deprecated Android API usages
    Overhauled UI
    Simplified navigation
    Dedicated "Now Playing" tab

1.13 - 2020-12-06
    Workaround for "limit=none" bug in Ampache API 4.2.5
    Caching playlist names

1.12 - 2020-11-24
    Workaround for "limit=none" bug in Ampache API 4.2.4
    Removed persistent notification

1.11.3 - 2020-11-20
    Added back support for 7 Nougat and 8 Oreo
    Android Auto functionality is disabled for now

1.11.2 - 2020-11-19
    Dropped support for older Android versions, minimum is now 9 Pie
    Night theme

1.11.1 - 2020-11-8
    Support for Google Play automated testing

1.11 - 2020-11-01
    Better handling of login errors

1.10 - 2020-10-31
    Quit automatically when Android Auto exists if persistent notification is on
    Clear cache on quit in an effort to prevent Android Auto from constantly changing album art
    Preparations for the highly anticipated Ampache version 5.0.0

1.9 - 2020-09-05
    Fade if track is tagged "Live", "Medley", or "Nonstop"
    Bugfixes:
        Automatic starts
        Error handling
        Quit

1.8 - 2020-03-29
    Options menu
    Seek bar
    Tap title to skip to any song in playlist/album

1.7 - 2020-02-29
    Loudness effect added to Equalizer (may require re-set of equalizer)
    Tap art to view zoomed image
    Bugfix:
        Better handling lost network connection

1.6 - 2020-02-24
    Bugfix:
        Corrected track count when reaching end of playlist or album

1.5 - 2020-02-23
    Smart lists always start from beginning
    Skip to previous in playlists and albums
    "Back to albums" button in Browse
    Bugfix:
        Stopping Amproid service

1.4 - 2020-02-18
    Fine tuned Google Assistant support

1.3 - 2020-02-16
    UI facelift
    Play entire albums from Browse
    Search
    Google Assistant support: "Hey Google, play <whatever_you_want_to_hear>"
    Bugfix:
        Better handling of error while starting to play

1.2 - 2020-01-26
    Accounts menu
    Better error messages
    Show track number when playing playlist
    Better displaying long titles
    Bugfixes:
        Audio Focus request on play
        Increased network timeout

1.1 - 2019-12-31
    Moved Equalizer to menu
    Added a persistent notification to help opening Amproid from within Android Auto (can be turned off)
    More pleasant notification sound at startup
    "About" info

1.0 - 2019-12-25
    Initial release


